{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "f95cb77f-b9f7-45e2-b7dc-053742b1e6ea",
    "name": "Turfzone API",
    "description": "Postman collection for the Turfzone Rust/Umbral backend.\n\nRun Authentication / Login first; its test script stores the returned bearer token in authToken. Protected requests inherit bearer authentication from the collection. Public routes and the Paystack provider webhook explicitly use no authentication.\n\nGoogle OAuth is browser-based. Configure UMBRAL_OAUTH_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID and UMBRAL_OAUTH_GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET, then use Google OAuth / Start Google Login in a browser. Provider discovery can be tested directly in Postman.\n\nPlayer workflows require a Player profile role (new auth users without a profile default to Player). Manager setup requires Manager or ManagerStaff. Admin/test-money routes require AuthUser.is_superuser. Generated REST requires auth staff or superuser and permits list/retrieve only.\n\nGenerated REST resource values: user_profile, manager_profile, staff_membership, venue, amenity, venue_amenity, field, field_image, opening_hours, availability_exception, booking, payment, refund, wallet, wallet_transaction, paystack_subaccount, payout, notification.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{authToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "pm.test(\"Response is not a server error\", function () {",
          "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.below(500);",
          "});"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
